WEBVTT

00:17.684 --> 00:20.145
My bad luck didn't start
in an Egyptian tomb.

00:22.147 --> 00:24.190
It didn't start in a Maya temple either.

00:25.275 --> 00:27.152
It started at a child's birthday party.

00:28.903 --> 00:32.323
As always, everything started with Lucy.

00:33.366 --> 00:34.576
My sister.

00:35.535 --> 00:38.538
Who simply smiled
and got anything she wanted.

00:38.621 --> 00:39.456
Lucy's cake!

00:39.539 --> 00:42.417
But to even out
what genetics have robbed me of,

00:42.500 --> 00:44.919
I had a kind of Machiavellian plan.

00:45.003 --> 00:46.504
Make a wish, Lucy!

00:47.464 --> 00:48.465
No!

00:49.632 --> 00:50.967
I stole your wish.

00:51.634 --> 00:55.305
Well I'm going to steal
all of your wishes forever.

00:57.807 --> 01:01.686
And from that day forward
everything changed.

01:01.770 --> 01:02.687
Everything.

01:02.771 --> 01:04.439
-Hi, Lucy
-Hi, Sara!

01:04.522 --> 01:06.399
-Is that her sister?
-I think so.

01:06.483 --> 01:09.903
Ugh. She was so annoying,
I begged my parents to change schools.

01:10.487 --> 01:11.321
Bye, Lucy.

01:11.404 --> 01:12.238
Bye, bad karma.

01:13.114 --> 01:14.449
Hello, Aarón.

01:15.366 --> 01:17.202
And everything was perfect.

01:17.285 --> 01:18.203
By the way,

01:18.745 --> 01:19.746
I have a surprise.

01:20.330 --> 01:21.164
Really?

01:22.082 --> 01:23.625
-Really.
-You made it yourself?

01:23.708 --> 01:24.709
Yes.

01:24.793 --> 01:27.253
Finally, Lucy's curse had ended.

01:28.546 --> 01:30.173
Sara, you're my…

01:30.673 --> 01:33.176
Love knocking at my door.

01:33.927 --> 01:36.054
You're my best friend.

01:36.554 --> 01:37.388
Or not.

01:37.472 --> 01:40.308
My string of bad luck wasn't over yet.

02:00.245 --> 02:01.621
Answer, I'm sure it's--

02:01.704 --> 02:02.539
My sister.

02:03.123 --> 02:04.707
They moved to Monterrey.

02:04.791 --> 02:05.959
I didn't see him again.

02:06.042 --> 02:06.876
SUBSCRIBE

02:06.960 --> 02:09.712
Aarón. My first real love.

02:11.339 --> 02:15.093
He had his first hit
and beat sales records.

02:15.927 --> 02:16.803
ARTIST OF THE YEAR

02:16.886 --> 02:19.097
He became super famous
and traveled the world.

02:20.890 --> 02:23.518
-Sara? Hi!
-Hello?

02:23.601 --> 02:25.854
And Lucy also became super famous.

02:25.937 --> 02:28.731
Her beauty captivated the catwalks

02:28.815 --> 02:31.734
and today she's the preferred model
for some big brands.

02:32.777 --> 02:35.613
They're both super famous and I…

02:35.697 --> 02:36.531
I am here.

02:37.532 --> 02:38.491
In Mérida.

02:40.034 --> 02:43.163
With a marvelous store that brings in--

02:43.246 --> 02:44.789
One thousand five hundred pesos.

02:44.873 --> 02:46.583
With that, we can buy more shirts

02:46.666 --> 02:47.834
and print more bombas.

02:47.917 --> 02:48.960
Look.

02:49.043 --> 02:50.003
It's a bomba.

02:51.504 --> 02:54.007
No, not a bomb that goes--

02:54.090 --> 02:55.258
And your brand?

02:55.341 --> 02:57.719
Sacni. That's a fantasy.

02:57.802 --> 02:59.762
You've settled, Sarita.

02:59.846 --> 03:01.764
Settled? How, Sacni?

03:01.848 --> 03:04.809
I'm living a stable life,

03:04.893 --> 03:05.727
a peaceful life…

03:05.810 --> 03:08.188
-In a crumbling house.
-…to get rid of my bad karma.

03:09.480 --> 03:12.609
I'm going to steal
all of your wishes forever.

03:15.778 --> 03:16.654
Sara?

03:22.118 --> 03:23.369
Sara?

03:24.662 --> 03:25.496
Sara!

03:26.789 --> 03:29.584
Open up, it's Lucy! Sister!

03:29.667 --> 03:31.002
A NETFLIX FILM

03:31.502 --> 03:32.670
I can't open this.

03:35.089 --> 03:39.260
My sister. The perfect one.
Always interrupting.

03:40.678 --> 03:41.721
Here it is.

03:41.804 --> 03:43.765
It's a Himalayan aquamarine.

03:44.265 --> 03:46.059
It's for good luck.

03:46.684 --> 03:48.853
Of which you've shamelessly robbed me?

03:49.979 --> 03:51.481
How thoughtful, thank you.

03:51.564 --> 03:54.192
Sari, I need an update.
I want to know everything.

03:54.275 --> 03:56.486
How's it going with Gilberto?
How's the boutique?

03:56.569 --> 03:57.487
Roberto.

03:57.570 --> 03:58.571
Hello!

03:58.655 --> 04:01.241
-I'll get it.
-Hello, my daughters!

04:01.324 --> 04:04.327
-Mommy and Daddy are here!
-This is gorgeous, Mom.

04:04.410 --> 04:07.372
With the heat here, it will be so nice.

04:07.455 --> 04:08.414
Hey, Sarita.

04:08.498 --> 04:10.833
Have you done anything
about your grandma's house?

04:10.917 --> 04:14.254
Everything's falling apart.
You said you'd remodel it.

04:14.337 --> 04:16.506
Okay. Weren't you two separating?

04:16.589 --> 04:17.548
I'm getting married.

04:18.299 --> 04:19.425
-You?
-You, married?

04:19.509 --> 04:20.343
You're separating?

04:20.426 --> 04:22.053
-No.
-Your mom has a lover.

04:22.136 --> 04:24.806
-She wants an open relationship.
-What do you mean open?

04:24.889 --> 04:27.517
I don't have a lover!
It's the idea of a lover.

04:27.600 --> 04:28.643
It's an internet fling.

04:28.726 --> 04:30.895
Think of the STDs you could get.

04:30.979 --> 04:32.355
Okay, are you pregnant?

04:32.438 --> 04:35.316
-No. I'm in love.
-She's gonna meet him in Mérida.

04:35.400 --> 04:36.943
He's gonna wear a green shirt.

04:37.026 --> 04:38.069
Look. Why--

04:38.152 --> 04:41.155
Hey, Lucia. Who are you marrying?
A woman or man?

04:41.239 --> 04:42.198
Don't change the topic.

04:42.282 --> 04:45.702
Why not let
your older sister get married first?

04:45.785 --> 04:46.911
Enough!

04:48.746 --> 04:50.498
Why don't I show you all to your rooms

04:50.581 --> 04:52.959
and we'll talk about all this tomorrow?

04:53.584 --> 04:55.003
-Okay.
-Let's go.

04:57.672 --> 04:58.798
I don't want a divorce.

05:06.055 --> 05:08.891
Hey, Sari.
Thanks for lending me your room.

05:08.975 --> 05:11.602
Between the news
about Mom and Dad and the jet lag,

05:11.686 --> 05:13.521
I need to rest.

05:18.484 --> 05:19.694
Need extra sheets?

05:19.777 --> 05:21.112
No, dude. What sheets?

05:21.195 --> 05:23.740
I sleep naked here.
This heat is killing me.

05:26.409 --> 05:29.662
I'm getting married!

05:30.204 --> 05:31.039
How cool!

05:32.540 --> 05:33.666
Now you?

05:33.750 --> 05:34.959
What are you doing, Dad?

05:35.585 --> 05:36.753
Your mother.

05:37.378 --> 05:39.297
She doesn't want me to sleep with her.

05:39.380 --> 05:40.214
Seriously?

05:41.090 --> 05:42.050
For real, Mom?

05:43.051 --> 05:44.635
You kicked Dad out of the room?

05:44.719 --> 05:45.553
That sucks, Mom.

05:46.346 --> 05:48.431
It's just that your dad is angry.

05:49.015 --> 05:52.560
With all this open relationship stuff,
he's unbearable.

05:52.643 --> 05:54.771
Come on, you both need to get over it.

05:55.563 --> 05:57.190
-Your daughter's marrying.
-Yeah.

05:57.273 --> 05:58.399
That's more important.

05:58.483 --> 06:01.611
Yes. And with that beauty and charisma,
it's about time.

06:01.694 --> 06:03.529
Not as late as others, right?

06:06.657 --> 06:08.117
Good night, Ma. Sleep tight.

06:08.201 --> 06:09.911
Sleep tight, my love. Thank you.

06:12.538 --> 06:14.582
-Can't you hear me?
-Tell her congratulations.

06:14.665 --> 06:15.500
What?

06:17.001 --> 06:18.211
Fuck, there's a delay.

06:19.045 --> 06:20.588
But, can you hear me, my love?

06:20.671 --> 06:23.508
Yes, perfectly. I was just saying that…

06:23.591 --> 06:27.929
That…

06:28.012 --> 06:28.846
…your parents.

06:29.347 --> 06:30.223
My parents?

06:30.848 --> 06:31.682
Yeah.

06:32.934 --> 06:33.768
Well…

06:34.519 --> 06:35.353
I don't know.

06:35.436 --> 06:39.023
That naturally,
with her charisma and beauty,

06:39.107 --> 06:41.692
it was past time and blah, blah--

06:43.111 --> 06:44.195
Lame.

06:44.779 --> 06:45.822
What did you say…?

06:45.905 --> 06:50.535
What…?

06:59.460 --> 07:01.045
Hurry up!

07:01.129 --> 07:02.630
He'll be here soon.

07:19.230 --> 07:20.064
Hi.

07:20.982 --> 07:22.066
You're Lucy's sister?

07:23.109 --> 07:23.985
I'm her fiancé.

07:24.694 --> 07:25.528
How are you?

07:26.612 --> 07:28.114
-Aarón?
-Sara?

07:29.949 --> 07:30.950
Sara!

07:32.743 --> 07:34.245
Is it really you?

07:34.328 --> 07:35.413
For real?

07:36.330 --> 07:37.707
Sarita!

07:38.416 --> 07:39.834
-Sara!
-I can't believe it.

07:40.960 --> 07:41.919
Is this for real?

07:42.003 --> 07:44.297
That… that you… actually…

07:44.380 --> 07:45.256
Are you really…

07:45.339 --> 07:46.674
My fiancé!

07:47.383 --> 07:48.468
My baby!

07:48.551 --> 07:49.677
Baby!

07:49.760 --> 07:51.345
I'm so excited you're here!

07:52.763 --> 07:55.725
The curse is real.
She's gonna end up with everything I want.

07:55.808 --> 07:58.269
This is a very important moment for me.

07:58.352 --> 07:59.812
Truthfully. You have no idea…

08:00.354 --> 08:01.856
Hey, Sari. Thank you.

08:01.939 --> 08:03.399
Sari, Aarón.

08:03.483 --> 08:05.234
-Aarón, Sari.
-You won't believe it.

08:06.152 --> 08:08.821
I need you to be best friends.

08:09.322 --> 08:11.157
We already were best friends!

08:11.240 --> 08:13.159
-What?
-Sari, sardine!

08:14.035 --> 08:15.786
-Come, Sarita.
-You know each other?

08:15.870 --> 08:16.704
Is this a joke?

08:16.787 --> 08:17.914
Good morning!

08:19.207 --> 08:20.458
-General.
-For real?

08:20.541 --> 08:22.043
-Don't you remember me?
-Morning.

08:22.126 --> 08:24.295
-Isn't that your best friend from--
-Yes!

08:24.378 --> 08:25.463
High school!

08:25.546 --> 08:26.547
-Yes!
-You are correct.

08:26.631 --> 08:28.132
Weren't you that shitty kid?

08:28.216 --> 08:29.800
Yes, but now I'm the shit!

08:29.884 --> 08:31.552
Stay for breakfast?

08:31.636 --> 08:32.553
That's why I came.

08:32.637 --> 08:36.057
How about you take a bath
and fix up your hair. No?

08:36.140 --> 08:37.808
What are you drinking?

08:38.392 --> 08:39.894
I'm going to make a mimosa.

08:40.728 --> 08:43.022
-Of course.
-That's how I breakfast.

08:44.649 --> 08:46.984
Sari, sardine!

08:47.068 --> 08:49.612
Sari, sardine!

08:49.695 --> 08:51.280
Aren't you eating, Sara?

08:53.115 --> 08:53.991
Sara!

08:54.575 --> 08:55.785
-I'm okay!
-Are you okay?

08:55.868 --> 08:58.579
This is what happens
when you don't take care of your house.

08:58.663 --> 08:59.830
Where will you sleep?

08:59.914 --> 09:01.374
-Me?
-With me. Where else?

09:01.457 --> 09:02.375
In my room?

09:03.709 --> 09:06.212
Wait a minute. I'll be quick. Just wait.

09:06.295 --> 09:07.588
Holy Mother.

09:07.672 --> 09:08.923
Are you really not hurt?

09:09.006 --> 09:10.591
-You okay?
-I need to hang up…

09:10.675 --> 09:12.134
No. All good. I'm fine.

09:12.218 --> 09:13.636
Why are you so nervous?

09:13.719 --> 09:15.054
Can I help with something?

09:16.097 --> 09:18.391
I'm not nervous. Why would I be?

09:18.474 --> 09:19.433
It's the caffeine.

09:19.517 --> 09:21.978
-All good. It's normal.
-Sara.

09:22.061 --> 09:23.563
Breathe. Please.

09:24.814 --> 09:25.648
Look.

09:26.524 --> 09:29.026
I know bullying at school
had a bad effect on you.

09:29.110 --> 09:29.944
Okay, but…

09:31.445 --> 09:32.738
Was it him?

09:33.322 --> 09:35.449
Of course it was.
That's why you're like this?

09:35.533 --> 09:37.910
Lucy, please. Seriously, relax.

09:38.411 --> 09:39.412
And nothing's wrong.

09:39.495 --> 09:41.372
Stay as long as you like.

09:41.455 --> 09:42.498
Your home is my home.

09:42.582 --> 09:44.208
I mean, my home is your home.

09:44.292 --> 09:45.167
All good, okay?

09:47.503 --> 09:49.213
Know what? I need one thing.

09:49.922 --> 09:51.507
Don't pretend like you know me,

09:51.591 --> 09:52.967
because you don't.

09:57.930 --> 09:58.931
Hey, Sacni.

09:59.015 --> 10:00.349
About how long?

10:01.267 --> 10:04.020
How long would it take
to sell off everything in the store?

10:04.103 --> 10:05.813
Can I have breakfast?

10:05.896 --> 10:08.065
I'm just thinking about leaving the city.

10:08.149 --> 10:09.775
-Why?
-Circumstances outside my control.

10:10.860 --> 10:12.862
Or, better yet, I'll leave the country.

10:13.738 --> 10:15.573
-The planet.
-What crawled up your butt?

10:16.657 --> 10:18.075
What are you doing here, Sara?

10:18.159 --> 10:19.452
I'll call you back.

10:21.245 --> 10:23.247
So, this was your grandma's house,

10:23.331 --> 10:24.540
and now it's your store?

10:25.207 --> 10:26.292
Yes.

10:26.375 --> 10:27.918
Truth is, I'm great.

10:28.002 --> 10:29.086
You too, right?

10:29.170 --> 10:30.630
I heard something about you.

10:30.713 --> 10:32.423
Are you a model or what?

10:32.506 --> 10:33.466
Model?

10:34.050 --> 10:34.884
Singer.

10:35.468 --> 10:37.678
-Soloist.
-Singer, sure.

10:38.179 --> 10:39.930
Well, I'm a businesswoman.

10:40.014 --> 10:43.142
"While walking through the cemetery,
I heard a skull shout,

10:43.225 --> 10:46.103
'If you're not gonna give it up,
at least whip it out.'" Bomba!

10:47.146 --> 10:49.190
They're selling like hotcakes.

10:50.524 --> 10:53.069
I always knew
you'd do something avant-garde.

10:53.152 --> 10:55.279
Well look at you, all famous. That's cool.

10:55.363 --> 10:56.489
Not as famous as you.

10:56.572 --> 10:58.240
Look, here come your fans.

10:58.324 --> 10:59.158
We're closed!

11:00.159 --> 11:00.993
Later.

11:02.036 --> 11:03.871
-Don't you need to open?
-No.

11:04.914 --> 11:05.748
-Sure?
-Yes.

11:06.332 --> 11:07.917
Aarón. Aarón what? Star?

11:08.000 --> 11:08.959
Aarón Star.

11:09.043 --> 11:09.919
Can you read it?

11:11.253 --> 11:12.129
Yes.

11:14.256 --> 11:17.843
Great. I'll leave you to attend
to your legion of fans.

11:17.927 --> 11:20.388
-Perfect, brother-in-law.
-Open up your store and…

11:23.182 --> 11:24.392
And…

11:24.475 --> 11:26.560
-We'll talk later.
-Later, brother-in-law.

11:27.311 --> 11:28.312
Go.

11:28.396 --> 11:29.605
-All right. Bye.
-Bye.

11:30.564 --> 11:31.691
Yoo-hoo.

11:32.400 --> 11:34.235
Are you open?

11:36.696 --> 11:37.780
Look, Sarita!

11:37.863 --> 11:40.574
Yucatán Fashion Fest.

11:40.658 --> 11:41.659
Okay, so are we going?

11:42.618 --> 11:45.663
No. You know I've left
such trivialities behind.

11:45.746 --> 11:47.289
You haven't even tried.

11:49.125 --> 11:51.001
I also can't believe

11:51.711 --> 11:53.462
that you believe in curses.

11:53.546 --> 11:54.630
And from your sister!

11:55.339 --> 11:56.173
Why?

11:57.091 --> 11:58.676
-Is she a witch?
-No, dude!

11:58.759 --> 11:59.927
Worse.

12:00.010 --> 12:01.053
She's a model.

12:01.137 --> 12:02.638
…designer Colavita…

12:02.722 --> 12:03.639
Here you are.

12:03.723 --> 12:04.974
Thanks.

12:05.057 --> 12:06.267
Cheers.

12:06.851 --> 12:09.687
You know that when I drink
I go crazy, so, no.

12:10.688 --> 12:13.107
Let it go. That's what you need to do.

12:13.190 --> 12:14.650
Dream again!

12:14.734 --> 12:15.818
My God. Really…

12:16.444 --> 12:18.404
Another time, definitely, all right?

12:18.487 --> 12:20.990
Right now, I just want to be alone.

12:21.073 --> 12:21.949
Alone.

12:22.658 --> 12:25.077
You don't know how happy it makes me

12:25.161 --> 12:27.371
that you can finally meet my family.

12:27.455 --> 12:28.789
-Who's she talking to?
-Look.

12:28.873 --> 12:32.042
-Her fans.
-She has fans?

12:32.126 --> 12:33.586
-Cheers, Mom.
-Cheers.

12:33.669 --> 12:35.671
Here's my dad. Say hi, Dad.

12:36.213 --> 12:38.048
So handsome with those sunglasses!

12:38.132 --> 12:39.884
And I'd like you to meet Sari,

12:39.967 --> 12:41.218
my older sister.

12:41.302 --> 12:45.723
Allow me to tell you
that she's the coolest designer there is.

12:45.806 --> 12:47.141
She's also my best friend.

12:47.224 --> 12:49.727
Since we were little,
people have said we're identical.

12:49.810 --> 12:50.853
What do you think?

12:50.936 --> 12:52.438
They got it from me.

12:52.521 --> 12:53.355
Yep.

12:53.981 --> 12:55.191
They're saying I'm ugly.

12:56.692 --> 12:57.526
Okay.

12:58.402 --> 13:00.196
The time has come.

13:00.279 --> 13:01.280
I'm very nervous.

13:01.363 --> 13:02.364
Okay.

13:02.448 --> 13:04.408
I'd like to share with you

13:04.492 --> 13:06.952
the reason I've decided
to gather with my family,

13:07.036 --> 13:09.079
including you, of course,

13:09.163 --> 13:11.665
in Mérida, my grandmother's homeland.

13:11.749 --> 13:12.958
May she rest in peace.

13:13.042 --> 13:14.376
Rest in peace.

13:14.460 --> 13:15.503
Baby.

13:15.586 --> 13:17.338
-Do you want to say or should I?
-You.

13:17.421 --> 13:19.048
-Are you sure?
-Yes, my love.

13:19.131 --> 13:20.883
I feel like I can't breathe.

13:20.966 --> 13:22.468
Okay. Here goes.

13:23.844 --> 13:25.471
My baby and I…

13:25.971 --> 13:27.556
got married!

13:28.808 --> 13:30.392
What? They're already married?

13:32.853 --> 13:33.687
Congratulations!

13:35.189 --> 13:36.482
Congratulations!

13:38.359 --> 13:39.193
Aarón!

13:39.902 --> 13:41.028
Aarón Star!

13:41.111 --> 13:42.446
Why are you hiding here?

13:43.489 --> 13:44.406
Do you agree

13:44.490 --> 13:47.910
that Aarón Star is officially
the worst artist name in the universe?

13:47.993 --> 13:49.495
My manager gave it to me.

13:49.578 --> 13:51.080
Who is your manager? Your mom?

13:52.039 --> 13:53.415
What the hell?

13:53.499 --> 13:54.583
And who are they?

13:55.125 --> 13:56.627
Some reggaeton dudes, I think.

13:57.461 --> 13:59.129
I like the Punk Flamingos more.

14:00.714 --> 14:01.549
Me too.

14:02.716 --> 14:03.592
Thank you!

14:04.218 --> 14:05.970
We're the Punk Flamingos!

14:06.470 --> 14:08.055
This is all thanks to you.

14:10.891 --> 14:11.976
Okay.

14:12.059 --> 14:12.893
Shall we?

14:13.394 --> 14:14.603
-Let's go.
-But that way.

14:15.145 --> 14:16.146
-Okay.
-Okay?

14:16.647 --> 14:17.690
You go that way.

14:17.773 --> 14:19.441
No, I'm saying you leave…

14:19.525 --> 14:21.318
Cover your face!

14:30.786 --> 14:31.996
You make Aarón laugh.

14:33.497 --> 14:34.498
-Me?
-Yes.

14:35.499 --> 14:37.918
I saw you running
out of the restaurant together…

14:39.253 --> 14:40.504
How'd you make him laugh?

14:42.631 --> 14:46.760
Well, you know better than anyone
